}}'''''Wooden Ships and Iron Men''''' is a [[computer wargame]] published by [[Avalon Hill]] in 1987 for the [[Commodore 64]].

==Gameplay==
This game is based on the [[naval]] [[board wargame]], ''[[Wooden Ships and Iron Men]]''. In the combat phase, the outcome of a battle is revealed when the winner is declared.<ref name="Dragon138"/>

